data.description: Absolutely stunning remodeled 6 year-old Decatur townhome. This home boasts 2 extra large bedrooms with adjoining baths, (roommate style). It also has hardwood floors and stairway and tile living room and den floors. Granite countertops and an open floor plan. New carpet in the bedrooms and bamboo in the  hallway helps keep unit extra clean. Home comes with stainless steel appliances and washer/dryer. Lots of upgrades in kitchen and bathrooms! This home made almost $10,000 in AirBNB rentals last year. Lots of closet space and one car garage excellent for EV. Bring Highest and Best offers! Owner/Agent
